snippet.title: Ricochet Kills 2 -50 levels
snippet.description: The second part of the game is where your bullets bouncing off the walls should touch people's ragdolls in black. Now our hero can also die, not from bullets but from blocks and platforms, which, can fall on us. In the game, fifteen levels, and for me, for example, the passage of all took about an hour.
